# Kräver VSCode tillägget Rest-Client (humao.rest-client)
@apiUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### Get all products
GET {{apiUrl}}

### Get one product
GET {{apiUrl}}/1002

### Create new product
POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jeans",
    "price": 49
}

### Update product info (put)
# PUT uppdaterar hela dataobjektet
PUT  {{apiUrl}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Shirt",
    "price": 29
}

### Update product info (patch)
# Patch kan uppdatera enskilda fält
PATCH  {{apiUrl}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 29
}

### Delete product
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/1004
